p: Identification of individual constituents was done by comparing the RI-values and mass spectra with data generated under similar conditions using a special two-dimensional search algorithm software with an integrated library, considering the RI and MS similarities [ 31]. Additionally, MassLib (1996–2008) was applied with other available libraries like Wiley Registry (4th ed.), NIST/EPA/NIH Mass spectral Library (2005) and the Adams Library [ 32]. Furthermore, available authentic reference compounds were used in the comparison. The determination of RI was attained based on a homologous n-alkanes series (C8–C30) under identical working conditions.
